     Set the read (and write) timeoutâ€”the same as â€˜--read-timeout=Nâ€™.

reclevel = N
     Recursion level (depth)â€”the same as â€˜-l Nâ€™.

recursive = on/off
     Recursive on/offâ€”the same as â€˜-râ€™.

referer = STRING
     Set HTTP â€˜Referer:â€™ header just like â€˜--referer=STRINGâ€™.  (Note
     that it was the folks who wrote the HTTP spec who got the spelling
     of â€œreferrerâ€ wrong.)

relative_only = on/off
     Follow only relative linksâ€”the same as â€˜-Lâ€™ (*note Relative
     Links::).

remote_encoding = ENCODING
     Force Wget to use ENCODING as the default remote server encoding.
     See â€˜--remote-encodingâ€™.

remove_listing = on/off
     If set to on, remove FTP listings downloaded by Wget.  Setting it
