     Choose the secure protocol to be used.  Legal values are â€˜autoâ€™
     (the default), â€˜SSLv2â€™, â€˜SSLv3â€™, and â€˜TLSv1â€™.  The same as
     â€˜--secure-protocol=STRINGâ€™.

server_response = on/off
     Choose whether or not to print the HTTP and FTP server
     responsesâ€”the same as â€˜-Sâ€™.

