     If set to â€˜offâ€™, Wget wonâ€™t set the local fileâ€™s timestamp by the
     one on the server (same as â€˜--no-use-server-timestampsâ€™).

tries = N
     Set number of retries per URLâ€”the same as â€˜-t Nâ€™.

